Welcome to JW Broadcasting. This month we focus on how we can refine ourselves as

00:00:09.099 --> 00:00:15.900
Christians by imitating Jehovah's Holiness. Do you sometimes say things you later

00:00:15.900 --> 00:00:22.339
regret? Something unkind perhaps critical of others? We'll learn from this

00:00:22.339 --> 00:00:29.899
dramatization how to adjust not only what we say but also how we think. If you're a

00:00:29.899 --> 00:00:37.460
young person, do you ever feel you're in a fight? A fight to please Jehovah? A fight

00:00:37.460 --> 00:00:45.619
to be joyful despite opposition? You'll enjoy our new music video. Some of Jehovah's

