people to return to him. We'll see how he helped this man turn his life around.

00:00:58.380 --> 00:01:25.659
All of this and more on JW Broadcasting for October 2019. When I say the words

00:01:25.659 --> 00:01:32.379
holy and holiness, what comes to your mind? Many think of words like clean and

00:01:32.379 --> 00:01:39.780
pure. But let's change the question a little. Who comes to your mind? Likely you

00:01:39.780 --> 00:01:46.019
think of Jehovah. You might also picture Jesus Christ and the Holy Angels. But do

00:01:46.019 --> 00:01:54.019
you think of imperfect humans? Can humans be described as holy? Yes. We know

00:01:54.019 --> 00:01:59.420
this because humans were created in God's image. Just as we can reflect godly

00:01:59.420 --> 00:02:06.739
qualities such as love, kindness and self-control, we can reflect holiness. How

00:02:06.739 --> 00:02:14.180
seriously should we take holiness? It's no small matter. Today the world around us

00:02:14.180 --> 00:02:20.979
is increasing in badness. 2 Timothy chapter 3 verse 13 warns that wicked men would advance

00:02:20.979 --> 00:02:27.460
from bad to worse. Undoubtedly, before the end, Satan's efforts to promote wickedness

00:02:27.460 --> 00:02:36.099
will intensify. So we must intensify our efforts to be holy and reject all badness.

00:02:36.580 --> 00:02:45.419
Who do you think are Satan's primary targets? We are. He and the demons are like a

00:02:45.419 --> 00:02:52.139
pack of hungry lions looking to devour us. Being a publisher of the good news is

00:02:52.139 --> 00:03:00.539
a privilege that Satan seeks to attack. Are you a parent with children? Do you think

00:03:00.539 --> 00:03:08.419
Satan wants you to become unclean? Yes. He knows that devouring a family head could

00:03:08.419 --> 00:03:16.099
weaken an entire family. In the congregation, Satan would love to devour you dear pioneers,

00:03:16.099 --> 00:03:22.139
ministerial servants and elders. Are you in the circuit work? A missionary? A

00:03:22.139 --> 00:03:29.699
Bethelite? What a sacred privilege. But remember, it also means that we have a big target

00:03:29.699 --> 00:03:37.259
on our back. Satan and the demons would love to penetrate our clean and holy position.

00:03:37.259 --> 00:03:45.900
Doing so could impact the kingdom work or stumble others. So we can't be complacent.

00:03:45.900 --> 00:03:54.740
We must intensify our efforts to reject all badness. Thus holiness is a vital topic.

00:03:54.740 --> 00:04:02.979
To that end, the theme for this month's program is perfecting holiness in God's fear.

